reviewText: I love the show
Sisterly
Love it. Wish it was on dvd

When this originally aired, my mom would walk in the room, roll her eyes, say, "Oh, it's the blonde show," and walk out. Different generations, different tastes. I accept your judgement Mother and still feel I lead a full life. Lest you worry, dear reader, my mother and I have a perfectly harmonious relationship, so long as I keep this "blonde show" and Gilmore Girls off the screens when I visit.

This show is pure, substance free fun full of lots of laughs, deserved and not so much.
I love Amanda Bynes and Jennie Garth!  I love this series - it makes me laugh! Great way to end my night.
I love this show!!! Get a bluray or DVD release please!!!!! I don't do "On Demand" purchases! This show is awesome enough to get a DVD release.
My screen cut off what I was actually ordering and before I could see the entire description of this, I had purchased it. My fault. I really wanted a DVD and not an online movie.

This would be great for Prime instant video. This really would be my deal breaker for continuing the subscription. I do get better shows here on Prime than Netflix, and would love to stay. But I'm dying for this show. It's fun, sweet, cheesy and I grew up watching it right after school. Bring it to instant video please!!!
Super funny, however cheesy. This is not as good as the third or fourth seasons but still pretty good. I still wish they released them on DVD though.
I have watched every episode of thia show. Like every other episode this one was very funny and amanda never fails to make me laugh out loud literally. Lol.
